org.jhotdraw.draw
Class PictImageInputFormat

java.lang.Object
  org.jhotdraw.draw.PictImageInputFormat
All Implemented Interfaces:
InputFormat
public class PictImageInputFormat
extends java.lang.Object
implements InputFormat

An input format for importing drawings using the image/x-pict format from the Mac OS X clipboard.

This class uses the prototype design pattern. A ImageHolderFigure figure is used as a prototype for creating a figure that holds the imported image.
